Knowband - Magento Mobile App Development
Ever felt the need to take your online Magento website business to the mobile platform? Knowband seamless Mobile App Builder solution for Magento stores makes the job seamless for every eCommerce store owners. 
Knowband is a featured and complete Mobile App solution for your Magento eCommerce stores. It brings the readymade framework Mobile App Builder which converts your online website into feature-rich Android and iOS mobile apps. The developed mobile apps are fully synchronized with the website and thus inventory/order management becomes way handy for you. Once you get the framework, our development team delivers the app in 1 day.  
So, if you are really looking forward to grab all the mobile market benefits and enhance the revenue of your store, Knowband's Magento mobile app is the perfect tool for you. All you need to do is to follow these simple steps to get your own app:
1. Get the Mobile App Builder plugin from store. 
2. Share the specifications and requirements with us. 
3. Our development team will share the apk and ipa files. 
4. Publish the same on the app store and Google Play store.   
